      "para_id": "Q000915.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , built his E-ĝidru , the temple of seven niches ."
